Installation Instructions
=========================

To use these Autoconf macros into your project, perform the following
operations:

  * Users should get the latest release versions of these macros from the
[GNU Autoconf Archive][gar].

[gar]: http://www.gnu.org/software/autoconf-archive/

  * Copy the macro files to the macro directory of your project, as speicfied
by the `AC_CONFIG_MACRO_DIRS` macro in `configure.ac`.

  * Check the macro dependencies described in the documentation and add
    them all to the same directory.

  * Use the macros in your `configure.ac`. 
